name: The Green Park Hotel Ankara
description:
Offering views of Ankara city, this upscale conference hotel is 8 km from Gençlik Parkı and 5 km from Anıtkabir, a mausoleum housing former President Mustafa Kemal Atatürk.
Refined, warmly decorated rooms come with city views, free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, as well as desks, minibars, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Suites add terraces. Room service is available 24/7.
There are 2 polished restaurants offering Turkish and international fare, including 1 with a bar. A breakfast buffet is an extra cost. Other amenities include a fitness center, an indoor pool and a spa, as well as a convention center with 15 meeting rooms.
address: Kızılırmak Mah, Balgat, 1443. Cd., 06520 Çankaya/Ankara, Türkiye

nearby_places.name: Anıtkabir

nearby_places.name: Museum of Anatolian Civilizations
nearby_places.description: Museum of artifacts from the Paleolithic era to the classical period, some displayed in a courtyard.

nearby_places.name: Ankara Castle
nearby_places.description: Ancient castle built on a rocky hilltop, offering panoramic views of the city in all directions.

nearby_places.name: Kocatepe Mosque
nearby_places.description: Built 1967–1987, this neoclassical Ottoman-style mosque is the city's largest, accommodating 24,000.

nearby_places.name: Haci Bayram Mosque
nearby_places.description: Landmark mosque that was built during the Ottoman era & is still in use today.

nearby_places.name: Gençlik Parkı
nearby_places.description: Vast recreational area with paved walks alongside a pond, shaded benches & a small amusement park.

nearby_places.name: Etnoğrafya Müzesi
nearby_places.description: Small, well-curated museum with Turkish folkloric artifacts, ceramics, woodwork & jewellery.

nearby_places.name: Rahmi M. Koc Museum Ankara

nearby_places.name: Atatürk Forest Farm

nearby_places.name: Museum of the War of Independence
nearby_places.description: Museum exhibiting weaponry & artifacts from war of independence in imposing, 2-story stone building.

nearby_places.name: Kuğulu Park

nearby_places.name: Cermodern
